<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>cart </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="cart.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.6.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0px;
        padding: 0px;
        background-color: #d2d0d0;
        overflow-x: hidden; 
    }
    
    /* Header styles */
    
    
    header.page-header {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        width: 100%;
        background-color: #09bd93; 
        z-index: 1000; 
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        margin-bottom: 50px;
        width: 97vw;
    }
    .page-header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #09bd93;
        
       
    }
    
    /* Logo styles */
    .page_logo  {
        height: 40px;
        width: auto;
         color: #0e1a1c;
        padding: 5px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-family:'Franklin Gothic Medium', 'Arial Narrow', Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .page_logo i {
        padding: 5px;
     font-size: 30px;
    
    }
    
    /* Search bar styles */
    .page_search form {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
    }
    
    .page_search input[type="text"] {
        padding: 5px;
        font-size: 13px;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        border-radius: 8px 0 0 8px;
        outline: none;
        width: 500px;
        height: 30px;
    }
    
    .page_search button {
        padding: 5px 10px;
        font-size: 14px;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        border-left: none;
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        background-color: #7cfffe;
        /* color: white; */
        height: 42px;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    
    .page_search button:hover {
        background-color: #00ffbf;
    }
    
    /* Header navigation links styles */
    .page-header div {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
    }
    
    .page-header div a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #ffffff;
        margin-left: 5px;
        font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    .page-header div i {
        margin-right: 5px;
        color: #ffffff;
    }
     
    #LoginButton{
        cursor: pointer;
        margin-right: 20px ;
        color: white;
    }
    a{
        color: black;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    /* Specific sections styles */
    .Upload, .offer, .cart, .sign_in {
        margin-left: 20px;
    }
    
    .Upload a, .offer a, .cart a, .sign_in a {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
    }
    
    .cartpart {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        background-color: white;
        margin: 20px;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 50px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        height: 520px;
        overflow-y: auto;
        position: relative;
        top: 110px;
    }
    
    .cartpart img {
        max-width: 500px;
        margin-right: 80px;
        border-radius: 40px;
    }
    
    .cartpart .content {
        max-width: 500px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        position: relative;
        left: 70px;
    }
    
    .cartpart h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    
    .cartpart button {
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        margin: 5px 5px 5px 0;
        border-radius: 5px;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    
    .cartpart button:hover {
        background-color: #566d86;
    }
    
    .cartpart p {
        margin: 10px 0;
        font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    .cartpart h3 {
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #333;
    }
    
    .cartpart h4 {
        display: inline;
        text-decoration: line-through;
        color: #888;
        font-weight: normal;
    }
    
    .cartpart li {
        margin: 5px 0;
        font-size: 16px;
    }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="page-header">
        <div class="page_logo"><i class="fa-solid fa-truck-medical"></i>
        <h2 style="color: white;">DotMeds</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="page_search">
            <form action="/search" method="get">
                <input type="text" name="query" placeholder="  Search for medicine & wellness products...">
                <button type="submit">Search</button>
            </form>
        </div> 
        <div class="Upload"><i class="fa-solid fa-file-arrow-up"></i>
        <a href="Upload">Upload</a>
        </div>
        <div class="offer"><i class="fa-solid fa-tag"></i>
            <a href="Offers">Offers</a>
        </div>
        <div class="cart"><i class="fa-solid fa-cart-shopping"></i>
            <a href="Cart">Cart</a>
        </div>
        <a href="http://localhost:3000/signup"><div id="LoginButton" class="sign_in"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-plus"></i>
            Sign in/Sign up
        </div></a>
    </header>
    <div class="cartpart">
        <img src="https://www.netmeds.com/images/product-v1/600x600/390855/volini_gel_75gm_46854_0_3.jpg" alt="cart_image">
        <div class="content">
            <h1>
               
Volini Gel 75gm

                </h1>
            <button class="small-button">device</button>
            <button class="small-button">management</button>
            <p>5.0 ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ (1 Ratings & 1 Reviews)</p>
            <br>
            <h3>Rs 276 <h4> MRP ₹600.00</h4></h3>
            <ul>
                <li>This product cannot be returned for a refund or exchange</li>
                <li>Mkt: Roche Diabetes Care India Pvt LTD</li>
                <li>Country of Origin: United States</li>
                <li>Delivery charges if applicable will be applied at checkout </li>
            </ul>
            <button class="add-to-cart-button">ADD TO CART</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
